%N A260954 Longest checkmates in chess with n pieces on board.
%C A260954 Results based on research on the Nalimov and Lomonosov Endgame Tablebases.
%C A260954 The results for 6 and 7 pieces ignore the 50-move rule.
%C A260954 FEN:
%C A260954 3 pieces,  28 moves: 8/8/8/1k6/8/8/K5P1/8 w - - 0 1
%C A260954 4 pieces,  43 moves: 8/5k2/2PK4/5r2/8/8/8/8 w - - 0 1
%C A260954 5 pieces, 127 moves: 8/8/8/8/1p2P3/4P3/1k6/3K4 w - - 0 1
%C A260954 6 pieces, 262 moves: 6k1/5n2/8/8/8/5n2/1RK5/1N6 w - - 0 1
%C A260954 7 pieces, 549 moves: 1n1k4/6Q1/5KP1/8/7b/1r6/8/8 w - - 0 1
